{"tid":927972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"傷殘有罪？","createTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T06:16:24.000Z","uid":69200,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4333030a4fc0d6f59f2faaa3f960f84681fca9","tid":927972,"uid":69200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁既，我係一位傷健人士，呢排真係想開始搵工，自力更生，由於無工作經驗，就開始請教響馬會工作既「朋友」，佢開初話會試下幫我，咁我去完interview ，佢哋都話冇問題，原本10號會簽約，點知今日呢位「朋友」忽然間WhatsApp 我，話我入職之後有排受，又柒頭前柒頭後咁，仲要歧視我（見圖）其實馬會係咪平等機會僱主黎，咁大既機構都唔<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/04/213329_773a3cfe2616ed126fa694e890d0d35b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F213329_773a3cfe2616ed126fa694e890d0d35b.png&h=0782156e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/04/213410_8c8b3dcbacc18611106a3fb0b506cf7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F213410_8c8b3dcbacc18611106a3fb0b506cf7c.png&h=e9b00632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會比機會傷殘人士，我傷殘就要比人笑比人睇唔起？我只係想自力更生，有錯？<br />\n呢位哥哥現職大角嘴埃華街投注站"},{"pid":"80d0cf92c25104c075a25830d48f0d33890f9b38","tid":927972,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"對話圖?"},{"pid":"1d417923ab7d63c9fab2158035ff5477dd4b062f","tid":927972,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"腦部傷殘？乜都唔講撚知你咩事"},{"pid":"5c75802350ef4a1c9711bf75e74d0ab2736ad65e","tid":927972,"uid":97451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63edd50f6aa37784e0613be98f981531881f9391","tid":927972,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70151a0fddeb8186799997a476ea7f4b6d2d8927","tid":927972,"uid":69200,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"80d0cf92c25104c075